songs.title: Mouth
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
It's been a long time coming, I've been shaky for days
I bite my tongue, but I'm sick of the wait
I gotta couple of keys I need you to play
It's so good to know you, I can't wait to show you

[Pre-Chorus]
My, my, my la-da-da-da-da-da-da-da
The feeling I get, the feeling I get
La-da-da-da-da-da-da-da
Get under my skin, come touch this

[Chorus 1]
Mouth, mouth, mouth
This mouth, mouth, mouth
My mouth, mouth, mouth
This mouth, mouth, mouth, my

[Verse 2]
It's been a long time coming, we still haven't yet
Be my prince and I'll be your corvette
The door's wide open, so let yourself in
Come in, come in, oh come in
It's so good to know you, I can't wait to show you

[Pre-Chorus]
My, my, my la-da-da-da-da-da-da-da
The feeling I get, the feeling I get
La-da-da-da-da-da-da-da
Get under my skin, come touch this

[Chorus 2]
Mouth, mouth, mouth
My mouth, mouth, mouth
My mouth, mouth, mouth
This mouth, mouth, mouth
My, my, my

[Bridge]
Ah, this could get messy
Ah, the way you impress me
It's so good to know you
I can't wait to show you

[Pre-Chorus]
My, my, my la-da-da-da-da-da-da-da
The feeling I get, the feeling I get
La-da-da-da-da-da-da-da
Get under my skin, come touch this

[Chorus 2]
Mouth, mouth, mouth
My mouth, mouth, mouth
My mouth, mouth, mouth
This mouth, mouth, mouth
My mouth, mouth, mouth
My mouth, mouth, mouth
My mouth, mouth, mouth
This mouth, mouth, mouth
